milestones.description: Grant Flower and Dave Houghton's 110-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 85 between Kevin Arnott and Andy Flower
This is the highest match aggregate (397) involving teams England & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Graham Gooch has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (123) for ENG, going past Allan Lamb
Zimbabwe's 14-run win against England is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 13-run win against Australia
